sourcesContent: let e=async e=>"undefined"!=typeof window&&"PaymentRequest"in window&&await new window.PaymentRequest([{supportedMethods:e}],{id:"0",total:{label:"Item",amount:{currency:"USD",value:"1.00"}}}).canMakePayment();const t=()=>e("https://apple.com/apple-pay"),a=()=>e("https://google.com/pay");export{t as isApplePayPotentiallyAvailable,a as isGooglePayPotentiallyAvailable};
